                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12705294" author="shalinmangar" created="Sat, 2 May 2009 14:41:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The NPE is due to IndexDeletionPolicyWrapper.getLatestCommit returning null.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A null check is added in this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12705322" author="shalinmangar" created="Sat, 2 May 2009 19:36:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;SnapShooter uses SimpleFSLockFactory instead of custom code for locking&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;If the snapshot directory failed to create, log an error instead of silently failing with IOException&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Log all IOExceptions instead of silently failing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12705565" author="shalinmangar" created="Mon, 4 May 2009 11:27:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Replaced usage of ReplicationHandler.closeNoExp  with IOUtils.closeQuietly&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Added statistics for Snapshooter &amp;#8211; displays start time, end time and number of file in last snapshot&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

</comment>
                            <comment id="12705660" author="shalinmangar" created="Mon, 4 May 2009 17:49:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed revision 771378.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also removed the custom file copy method with FileUtils.copyFileToDirectory method.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12705662" author="shalinmangar" created="Mon, 4 May 2009 17:52:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Editing the name of the issue because it has many more changes rather than just a NPE fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12775727" author="gsingers" created="Tue, 10 Nov 2009 15:52:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bulk close for Solr 1.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
